  - profile: {fileID: -8844993947990760528, guid: 1979baf0d53bcc148ab8e133946026d7, type: 3}
    Character: Steph
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: "\xBFPor qu\xE9 corres?"
    - language: 1
      text: Hi. I'm Stephanie... but my friends calls me Steph!
  - profile: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98e98bdd8e6df0b49aa718e67b45b96e, type: 3}
    Character: Greg
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: ah...
    - language: 1
      text: ah...
  - profile: {fileID: -8844993947990760528, guid: 1979baf0d53bcc148ab8e133946026d7, type: 3}
    Character: Steph
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: Para que los zombies no te ataquen solo tienes que bailar!
    - language: 1
      text: 'Let''s start '
  - profile: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 98e98bdd8e6df0b49aa718e67b45b96e, type: 3}
    Character: Greg
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: No se bailar...
    - language: 1
      text: No se bailar...
  - profile: {fileID: -8844993947990760528, guid: 1979baf0d53bcc148ab8e133946026d7, type: 3}
    Character: Steph
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: "Eso no es bailar!. Mira te ense\xF1ar\xE9."
    - language: 1
      text: "Eso no es bailar!. Mira te ense\xF1ar\xE9."
  - profile: {fileID: -8844993947990760528, guid: 1979baf0d53bcc148ab8e133946026d7, type: 3}
    Character: Steph
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: "Estos zombies siempre repiten los mismos bailes. Con cuatro pasos estar\xE1s
        bien."
    - language: 1
      text: Estos zombies siempre repiten los mismossdsd pasos. Con cuatro pasos
        basta para sobrevivir.
  - profile: {fileID: -8844993947990760528, guid: 1979baf0d53bcc148ab8e133946026d7, type: 3}
    Character: Steph
    texts:
    - language: 0
      text: Empecemos aplaudiendo arriba!
    - language: 1
      text: 'Let''s start '
